# Agent-eval pipeline (T6.c — 2026-05-17):
# results/ is regenerated by every `npm run agent-eval` invocation; commit
# only baselines/ which are the manually-blessed reference scores. The
# synthetic test_regression_gate_synth.json artefacts are produced by
# src/__tests__/agent-eval-gate.spec.ts and are also volatile.
